{
  "content": "<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What is the SBA 7(a) Loan Program?</h2>\n              <div class=\"prose prose-lg max-w-none\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                  The SBA 7(a) loan program is the Small Business Administration's\n                  primary and most flexible loan program. It provides government-backed\n                  financing to small businesses that might not qualify for conventional\n                  loans, offering more favorable terms and lower barriers to entry.\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4\">\n                  The \"7(a)\" refers to Section 7(a) of the Small Business Act,\n                  which authorizes the SBA to guarantee loans made by participating\n                  lenders. The SBA doesn't lend money directly—instead, it guarantees\n                  75-85% of the loan, reducing risk for banks and enabling them to\n                  offer better terms to borrowers.\n                </p>\n                <div class=\"bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4 my-6\">\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                    <strong>Key Advantage:</strong> SBA 7(a) loans typically require only\n                    10-15% down payment compared to 20-30% for conventional loans, and\n                    offer repayment terms up to 25 years vs 5-10 years conventionally.\n                    This dramatically improves cash flow for growing businesses.\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Who is Eligible for SBA 7(a) Loans?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                SBA 7(a) eligibility is based on business size, operational history,\n                creditworthiness, and intended use of funds. Most for-profit small\n                businesses operating in the United States qualify.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Basic Eligibility Requirements\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span><strong>For-profit business</strong> – operating legally in the US</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span><strong>Meets SBA size standards</strong> – industry-specific</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span><strong>Owner equity injected</strong> – personal investment</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span><strong>Exhausted other options</strong> – conventional credit unavailable</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span><strong>Good character</strong> – no defaulted government debt</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Ineligible Businesses\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2\">\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Gambling establishments and casinos</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Lending or investment businesses</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Real estate investment (passive)</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Non-profit organizations</span>\n                      </li>\n                      <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                        <span>Businesses primarily engaged in speculation</span>\n                      </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"mt-6 bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Credit Requirements:</strong> While there's no official\n                  minimum credit score, most lenders prefer 680+ for 7(a) loans. Some\n                  SBA Express lenders may work with scores as low as 620.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What are SBA 7(a) Loan Amounts & Terms?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                SBA 7(a) loans offer flexible terms based on the intended use of funds.\n                The combination of high loan amounts, long terms, and competitive rates\n                makes this one of the most attractive small business financing options.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-blue-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Loan Use</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Maximum Term</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Interest Rate</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Real Estate</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">25 years</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Prime + 2.25-2.75%</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Equipment</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">10 years (or useful life)</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Prime + 2.25-2.75%</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Working Capital</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">10 years</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Prime + 2.25-4.75%</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Business Acquisition</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">10 years</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Prime + 2.25-2.75%</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Maximum Amount</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-green-600 font-bold\" colSpan={2}>$5,000,000</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border border-green-200\">\n                  <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-2 text-green-800\">SBA Guarantee Rates</h4>\n                  <ul class=\"text-sm space-y-1\">\n                    <li>• Loans up to $150,000: 85% guarantee</li>\n                    <li>• Loans over $150,000: 75% guarantee</li>\n                    <li>• SBA Express: 50% guarantee</li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg border border-blue-200\">\n                  <h4 class=\"font-bold mb-2 text-blue-800\">Down Payment</h4>\n                  <ul class=\"text-sm space-y-1\">\n                    <li>• Standard: 10-20%</li>\n                    <li>• Business acquisition: 10-15%</li>\n                    <li>• Start-ups: May require 20-30%</li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What Can SBA 7(a) Loans Be Used For?</h2>\n              <p class=\"text-gray-700 mb-6\">\n                SBA 7(a) loans are highly flexible—most legitimate business purposes\n                qualify. This versatility is one of the program's biggest advantages.\n              </p>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-green-50 rounded-lg border border-green-200\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center text-green-800\">\n                    Eligible Uses\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Working capital and operational expenses</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Equipment purchases and leasehold improvements</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Real estate acquisition or construction</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Business expansion or new location</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Inventory and supplies</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Debt refinancing (some restrictions)</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Business acquisition or partner buyout</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-red-50 rounded-lg border border-red-200\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center text-red-800\">\n                    Ineligible Uses\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Repaying delinquent taxes</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Reimbursing owners for prior investments</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Speculative investments</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Political or lobbying activities</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Pyramid sales or multi-level marketing</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What are the Types of SBA 7(a) Loans?</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-6\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      Standard 7(a) Loan\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-blue-700\">Up to $5M</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Maximum</div>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-green-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-green-700\">75-85%</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Guarantee</div>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-purple-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-purple-700\">5-10 days</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">SBA Response</div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                      The flagship 7(a) program for larger financing needs. Full SBA\n                      review required, but most flexible terms available.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      SBA Express\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-blue-700\">Up to $500K</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Maximum</div>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-green-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-green-700\">50%</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Guarantee</div>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-purple-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-purple-700\">36 hours</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">SBA Response</div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                      Fastest SBA loan option. Lenders use their own credit analysis,\n                      resulting in quicker decisions. Great for working capital needs.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      CAPLines\n                    </h3>\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4\">\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-blue-700\">Up to $5M</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Maximum</div>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-green-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-green-700\">75-85%</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Guarantee</div>\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"text-center p-3 bg-purple-50 rounded\">\n                        <div class=\"font-bold text-purple-700\">Revolving</div>\n                        <div class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">Structure</div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                      Revolving lines of credit for seasonal or cyclical working\n                      capital needs. Draw and repay as needed within the credit limit.\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Do You Apply for an SBA 7(a) Loan?</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-6\">\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">1</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Prepare Your Financials (2-4 weeks)</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Gather personal and business financial statements, tax returns,\n                      and create financial projections. Strong documentation is\n                      essential for approval.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">2</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Find an SBA Lender</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Look for SBA Preferred Lenders (PLP) in your area—they have\n                      delegated authority to approve loans faster. Use the SBA Lender\n                      Match tool to find options.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">3</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Submit Application Package</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Complete SBA Form 1919 and lender-specific application. Include\n                      business plan, purpose of loan, and detailed financial\n                      documentation.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">4</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Lender Review & SBA Approval (2-8 weeks)</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      The lender evaluates your application first. If approved, they\n                      submit to SBA for guarantee authorization (unless PLP lender,\n                      who can approve themselves).\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex items-start p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4\">5</div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Closing & Funding</h3>\n                    <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                      Sign loan documents, provide any required collateral, and receive\n                      funds. The entire process typically takes 30-90 days from\n                      application to funding.\n                    </p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What Documents Are Required for SBA 7(a)?</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                    Financial Documents\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Business tax returns (3 years)</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Personal tax returns (3 years)</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Year-to-date financial statements</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Personal financial statement (SBA Form 413)</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Bank statements (3 months)</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-4 flex items-center\">\n                    Business Documents\n                  </h3>\n                  <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\">\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Business plan with projections</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Business licenses and permits</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Articles of incorporation/organization</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Lease agreements</span>\n                    </li>\n                    <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <span>Accounts receivable/payable aging</span>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">How Long Does SBA 7(a) Approval Take?</h2>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto mb-6\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-blue-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Phase</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Timeline</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Notes</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Document Preparation</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">2-4 weeks</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Before application</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Lender Review</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">2-4 weeks</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Credit analysis</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">SBA Authorization</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">5-10 business days</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">For non-PLP lenders</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Closing</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">1-2 weeks</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Documentation</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold\">Total Process</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-bold\">30-90 days</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Typical range</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-yellow-50 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> SBA Express loans can close in as little as\n                  2-3 weeks. If speed is critical, consider Express for amounts under\n                  $500,000.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">What Common Mistakes Delay or Deny SBA Loans?</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">1</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Incomplete Financial Documentation</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Missing tax returns, outdated financials, or inconsistencies\n                          between documents are the #1 cause of delays. Prepare complete\n                          packages before applying.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">2</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Weak Cash Flow Projections</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Lenders need to see that your business can service the debt.\n                          Projections must be realistic, well-supported, and demonstrate\n                          adequate cash flow coverage.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">3</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Personal Credit Issues</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          Outstanding tax liens, recent bankruptcies, or undisclosed\n                          credit problems sink applications. Address credit issues\n                          before applying.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"flex items-start\">\n                      <div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0\">\n                        <span class=\"text-red-600 font-bold\">4</span>\n                      </div>\n                      <div>\n                        <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg\">Insufficient Owner Equity</h3>\n                        <p class=\"text-gray-600 mt-1\">\n                          SBA requires owners to have \"skin in the game.\" Inadequate\n                          owner investment or asking for 100% financing is rejected.\n                        </p>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">SBA 7(a) vs Conventional Business Loans</h2>\n              <div class=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n                <table class=\"w-full border-collapse border border-gray-200 mb-6\">\n                  <thead>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-blue-50\">\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Factor</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">SBA 7(a)</th>\n                      <th class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-left\">Conventional</th>\n                    </tr>\n                  </thead>\n                  <tbody>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Down Payment</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-green-600\">10-20%</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">20-30%</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Maximum Term</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-green-600\">10-25 years</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">5-10 years</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Prepayment Penalty</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-green-600\">None (after 3 years)</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Often yes</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"bg-gray-50\">\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Collateral Required</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-green-600\">Flexible</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">Typically 100%+</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold\">Approval Speed</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3\">30-90 days</td>\n                      <td class=\"border border-gray-200 px-4 py-3 text-green-600\">1-4 weeks</td>\n                    </tr>\n                  </tbody>\n                </table>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-500 p-4\">\n                <p class=\"text-gray-700\">\n                  <strong>Bottom Line:</strong> SBA 7(a) loans are almost always\n                  better if you qualify—lower down payment, longer terms, and more\n                  flexibility. The tradeoff is a longer approval process.\n                </p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Alternative SBA Loan Programs</h2>\n              <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">SBA 504 Loans</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Fixed-rate financing for major fixed assets like real estate and\n                    heavy equipment. Lower down payments (10%).\n                  </p>\n                  <a href=\"/blog/sba-loans-grants-guide\">\n                    SBA 504 Guide →\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">SBA Microloans</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Small loans up to $50,000 for startups and small businesses.\n                    Easier qualification than 7(a).\n                  </p>\n                  <a href=\"/blog/sba-microloans-complete-guide\">\n                    Microloan Guide →\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">SBA Disaster Loans</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Low-interest loans for businesses affected by declared disasters.\n                    Direct SBA lending.\n                  </p>\n                  <a href=\"/blog/sba-disaster-relief-loans-guide\">\n                    Disaster Loans Guide →\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"p-6 bg-white rounded-lg border\">\n                  <h3 class=\"font-bold text-lg mb-3\">SBIR/STTR Grants</h3>\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm mb-3\">\n                    Non-repayable R&D grants for tech companies. No repayment\n                    required—true grant funding.\n                  </p>\n                  <a href=\"/blog/sbir-sttr-complete-guide\">\n                    SBIR/STTR Guide →\n                  </a>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n<h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold mb-6\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\n              <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                {faqData.map((faq, index) => (\n                  <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                    <div class=\"card p-6 border rounded-lg mb-6 shadow-sm\">\n                      <h3 class=\"font-bold flex items-start\">\n                        {faq.question}\n                      </h3>\n                      <p class=\"text-gray-700 mt-2 ml-7\">{faq.answer}</p>\n                  </div>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          \n\n",
  "shortAnswer": "To apply for SBA 7(a) Loans Complete Guide 2026, start by reviewing the eligibility criteria and preparing a project proposal. Complete guide to SBA 7(a) loans. Learn eligibility requirements, application process, terms, and how to secure up to $5M in SBA funding for your business. Funding available: up to $5M.",
